    <summary>
      MegaCityOne is an authorization library that plugs into any kind of
      authentication system available. You can use JudgeDredd to handle your
      laws defined as lambda expressions or JudgeAnderson if your are the
      server-side JavaScript kind. Sets System.Web.HttpContext.Current.User
      (Web application) or System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal (desktop app)
      after user authentication and the judge you choose will be ready to go.
      You can also define your own Judge by Implementing the AbstractJudge. You
      are The Law!
    </summary>
